# Phase Planning

Never jump randomly. Always build according to the roadmap in [chatbotmaker-docs — Docs/05-mvp-roadmap.md](https://github.com/vishnutvm/chatbotmaker-docs/blob/master/Docs/05-mvp-roadmap.md).

## Build Order

```text
Phase 1  — Foundation (monorepo, CI, infra scaffold)
Phase 2  — Authentication
Phase 3  — Organizations
Phase 4  — AI
Phase 5  — Knowledge (RAG)
Phase 6  — Assistants
Phase 7  — Widget
Phase 8  — Billing
Phase 9  — Analytics
Phase 10 — Production hardening
```

## Rules

- **Never skip phases** — e.g. do not build Knowledge (Phase 5) before Authentication (Phase 2).
- **Never build Phase N+1** dependencies before Phase N exit criteria are met.
- When scoping work, state which phase and roadmap task it belongs to.
- If a request conflicts with phase order, explain the dependency and propose the correct sequence.
